---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import StackDiagram from "../components/StackDiagram.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="The Open-Source AI Stack">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-4">
    <p
      class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-subtle)] mb-4"
    >
      A living map &middot; updated daily
    </p>
    <h1
      class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text)] mb-6"
    >
      The Open-Source AI Stack
    </h1>
    <p
      class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-prose"
    >
      Nine core layers, five cross-cutting meta-layers, and the projects,
      news, and funding flowing through each. Updated once a day at 08:00
      Pacific by a scheduled agent that reads about thirty layer-specific
      feeds, dedupes, and routes each item to the layer it affects.
    </p>
  </section>

  <StackDiagram />

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 my-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="/today"
      class="block border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors bg-[var(--color-surface)] no-underline hover:no-underline group"
    >
      <p
        class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-subtle)] mb-2"
      >
        Today
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-2">
        What moved at each layer today
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        Per-layer roundup. One editorial paragraph, then layer-by-layer items
        with citations. Yesterday and the week archive linked from the page.
      </p>
    </a>
    <a
      href="/grants"
      class="block border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors bg-[var(--color-surface)] no-underline hover:no-underline group"
    >
      <p
        class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-subtle)] mb-2"
      >
        Grants
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-2">
        Who funds what, and where the gaps are
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        Active funders. Recently funded projects with layer attribution.
        Underfunded areas and concrete project shapes for new grantees.
      </p>
    </a>
    <a
      href="/predictions"
      class="block border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors bg-[var(--color-surface)] no-underline hover:no-underline group"
    >
      <p
        class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-subtle)] mb-2"
      >
        Predictions
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-2">
        We track our own calls
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        Falsifiable predictions per layer with horizons and resolution
        criteria. Filed publicly. Resolved openly. Vibes excluded.
      </p>
    </a>
    <a
      href="/about"
      class="block border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors bg-[var(--color-surface)] no-underline hover:no-underline group"
    >
      <p
        class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-subtle)] mb-2"
      >
        About
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl text-[var(--color-text)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-2">
        How this site is built and updated
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        Open methodology. The scheduled agent that maintains the site, the
        source feeds it reads, and the editorial rules it follows.
      </p>
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
